DTSTART:20260217T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Come learn about Zotero citation manager. A free\, open-source 
	citation management tool\, great for keeping your course readings and cita
	ble research materials organized in one place\, and helping prepare draft 
	citations for whatever citation style may be required of you. Zotero integ
	rates with web browsers for easy extraction of citable metadata for most r
	esources\, and integrates with Microsoft word seamlessly to help you more 
	easily integrate citations as you go through your writing process.
