BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:A-fqntOXS-TAVmxVsFbjM
SUMMARY:GenX Queer Coworking
DTSTAMP:20260214T003546Z
DTSTART:20260220T213000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description Bring your work project\, school project or creativ
	e project and hang out while working. Or bring some reading to catch up on
	. This space centers queer GenXers and is also open to GenX allies and 2SL
	GBTQIA\\+ queer folk from other age groups. Hosted on third Fridays\, 1:30
	-4pm\, at rotating Eastside locations. We may take a break for holidays. P
	lease check Pride Across the Bridge Website for updates. Masks encouraged 
	to keep our community safe! No refreshments are provided in this space\, b
	ut attendees can bring closed drink containers or dry snacks for personal 
	consumption. Third Fridays\, 1:30-4pm\, at rotating Eastside locations: 2/
	20/2026\, Redmond Library's small conference room. Transit options: Bus li
