SUMMARY:Beyond Binary Connections
DTSTAMP:20260214T003546Z
DTSTART:20260226T223000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description Come as you are to this bimonthly no-expectations s
	ocial space for our transgender and non-binary community. Enjoy good food\
	, board and card games\, and chill conversation with others in the queer c
	ommunity. You are also welcome to bring a book to read or an art project t
	o work on while quietly enjoying the company of other gender-diverse folks
	. Feel free to bring a game of your own to share or just hang out and chat
	! Each meet-up will be at a different location\, so sign up for Pride Acro
	ss the Bridge newsletter or watch our website. Masks are encouraged to kee
	p our community safe! All ages are welcome to come. This space is led by o
	ur Good Vibes Fairy\, Milo! Please observe our general event rules. Snacks
	 and drinks are occasionally provided in this space. -This is a safe space
	 for all. Any behavior that goes against the 2SLGBTQIA\\+ and BIPOC commun
	ity will result in an individual being asked to leave. -All ages are welco
	me\, but we ask minors or other folks who are under legal guardianship be 
	accompanied by a guardian or friend when attending this social event. Yout
	h can be accompanied by another youth. Guardians\, friends or caretakers d
	on't need to be transgender or non-binary. Find more information at: .
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/beyond-binary-connections
	/16924855/2026-02-26T00
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
